<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>You have requested to change your password, and you can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token, host: [@resource.organization.slug, '.',JoshIntranet::Application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]].join) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
